\par
Nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng l\u7901?i n\f0\lang1033\'e0y kh\'edch l\f1\lang1066\u7879? ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i nghe h\f0\lang1033\'e3y ki\'ean tr\'ec v\'e0 lu\'f4n ti\f1\lang1066\u7871?n v\u7873? ph\f0\lang1033\'eda tr\f2\u432?\f1\lang1066\u7899?c, b\u7845?t k\u7875? kh\f0\lang1033\'f3 kh\f2\'e3n.\par
\par
\b\fs50 4. S\f1\lang1066\u7917? D\u7909?ng Ng\f0\lang1033\'f4n T\f1\lang1066\u7915?\b0\fs30\par
S\u7917? d\u7909?ng t\u7915? ng\u7919? linh ho\u7841?t v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\'e1ng t\f1\lang1066\u7841?o \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? mi\f0\lang1033\'eau t\f1\lang1066\u7843? c\f0\lang1033\'e2u chuy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n m\u7897?t c\f0\lang1033\'e1ch s\f1\lang1066\u7889?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7897?ng. H\f0\lang1033\'e3y ch\'fa \'fd \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7871?n vi\u7879?c ch\u7885?n l\u7921?a t\u7915? \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? t\u7841?o ra s\u7921? k\u7871?t n\u7889?i c\u7843?m x\f0\lang1033\'fac v\f1\lang1066\u7899?i ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i nghe. \f2\'d0\f1\u7915?ng ng\u7841?i th\u7917? nghi\u7879?m v\u7899?i c\f0\lang1033\'e1c bi\f1\lang1066\u7879?n ph\f0\lang1033\'e1p tu t\f1\lang1066\u7915? nh\f2\u432? \f1\u7849?n d\u7909?, ho\f0\lang1033\'e1n d\f1\lang1066\u7909? v\f0\lang1033\'e0 so s\'e1nh \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7875? l\f0\lang1033\'e0m phong ph\'fa th\'eam l\f1\lang1066\u7901?i nh\u7841?c c\u7911?a b\u7841?n.\par
\par
\b\fs50 5. T\u7841?o S\u7921? K\u7871?t N\u7889?i\par
\b0\fs30 M\u7897?t b\f0\lang1033\'e0i nh\f1\lang1066\u7841?c rap th\f0\lang1033\'e0nh c\'f4ng c\f1\lang1066\u7847?n ph\u7843?i k\u7871?t n\u7889?i v\u7899?i ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i nghe qua c\f0\lang1033\'e2u chuy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n c\u7911?a n\f0\lang1033\'f3. H\'e3y chia s\f1\lang1066\u7867? nh\u7919?ng tr\u7843?i nghi\u7879?m, c\u7843?m x\f0\lang1033\'fac th\f1\lang1066\u7853?t c\u7911?a b\u7841?n \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? ng\f2\u432?\f1\u7901?i nghe c\u7843?m th\u7845?y g\u7847?n g\f2\u361?i v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\f1\lang1066\u7891?ng c\u7843?m.\par
\par
K\u7871?t Lu\u7853?n\par
Vi\u7879?c s\u7855?p x\u7871?p b\u7889? c\u7909?c c\f0\lang1033\'e2u chuy\f1\lang1066\u7879?n v\f0\lang1033\'e0 \f2\'f0\u432?a n\f0\'f3 v\'e0o l\f1\lang1066\u7901?i nh\u7841?c l\f0\lang1033\'e0 m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t b\f2\u432?\f1\u7899?c quan tr\u7885?ng \f2\'f0\f1\u7875? t\u7841?o n\f0\lang1033\'ean m\f1\lang1066\u7897?t b\f0\lang1033\'e0i h\'e1t rap \f1\lang1066\u7845?n t\f2\u432?\f1\u7907?ng v\f0\lang1033\'e0 s\'e2u s\f1\lang1066\u7855?c. H\f0\lang1033\'e3y th\f1\lang1066\u7921?c h\f0\lang1033\'e0nh nh\f1\lang1066\u7919?ng k\u7929? thu\u7853?t n\f0\lang1033\'e0y v\'e0 t\'ecm ra phong c\'e1ch ri\'eang c\f1\lang1066\u7911?a b\u7841?n.\f0\lang1033\par
